{"tid":604215,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇去過土耳其自由行既師兄?","createTime":"2018-03-24T13:12:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T10:17:27.000Z","uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c94a26993713bd6c0228adc7ed517a4010917de","tid":604215,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T13:12:38.000Z","msg":"10月出發 預11日 玩唔玩得晒全國 見佢要坐內陸機都幾煩咁..<br />\n有冇咩伏既景點? 打個底 再決定去唔去<br />\n<br />\n綿堡出名但聽聞冇晒水 得D人工池<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到既伊斯坦堡留3日<br />\n去坐熱氣球<br />\n番紅花城<br />\n<br />\n一丁麻甩佬去 睇古蹟 風景最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再食下野咁 <br />\n<br />\nthanks thanks"},{"pid":"e56f5f867a39d5ca91a33cbbdbe104b797e7d515","tid":604215,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T16:36:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13193cbda429636081597cdbacbd42556bff62e","tid":604215,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"想去ISIS？<br />\n安已不<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2033b8b062474ae13d99980d34a398f624b80c71","tid":604215,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T16:38:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/showthread.php?t=2837&amp;page=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.backpackers.com.tw%2Fforum%2Fshowthread.php%3Ft%3D2837%26page%3D8&d=ZU2mIAMeqG50Epqbz%2BTAa7r9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=37dace2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.backpackers.com.tw/forum/showthread.php?t=2837&amp;page=8</a><br />\n<br />\n騙人到酒吧喝酒,然後討以巨款的仙人跳的事,許多地方,很早就屢屢發生, 尤以環地中海岸國家 (西班亞,義大利,希臘,土耳其等)為然。我兩次在機場捷運被扒手扒, 也是在雅典與羅馬。<br />\n<br />\n我一直很不解,這些國家,旅遊佔其GDP很重要部份,但卻聽任這種詐騙甚至偷扒的事天天在那兒上演,旅遊警察,行同虚設,要是在台灣日本,萬一有這種事情爆了光,警方怕不馬上派人臥底清查,現在裝攝像鏡頭很容易, 在觀光區,那些歹徒在那兒生事,都是輕而易舉可找出來的,但是這些國家聽任觀光客被宰,實在可羞可恨。<br />\n記得二十年前,在伊斯坦堡的 Tasim 街上, 就是每走不到一個街口,就有人過來想和你搭話,甚至還有斯利蘭卡人呢!想想看, 我們東方人在那兒,一看就是外國人,竟然會有人呆到用英文來問你路或時間嗎?為什麼不去問滿大街的當地人? 會有好康事發生嗎?"},{"pid":"5ea0f87ae40ea5ce38f5fcdc309214dcafe89b60","tid":604215,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"所以盡量方便自由行既國家就好d<br />\n呢D 自己包車 之類... 好易中伏"},{"pid":"e077471c4dbb2b36d56fe0abf1c437f4e3186fc5","tid":604215,"uid":27008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T17:55:04.000Z","msg":"記得如果有人主動用英文聊你叫你一齊去飲酒  唔好理佢地<br />\n<br />\n利申去過istanbul 成日有人聊"},{"pid":"33401a2581d49203ce3a9f7ca8ca64299fbe3b4e","tid":604215,"uid":96107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c94a26993713bd6c0228adc7ed517a4010917de","tid":604215,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T13:12:38.000Z","msg":"10月出發 預11日 玩唔玩得晒全國 見佢要坐內陸機都幾煩咁..<br />\n有冇咩伏既景點? 打個底 再決定去唔去<br />\n<br />\n綿堡出名但聽聞冇晒水 得D人工池<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到既伊斯坦堡留3日<br />\n去坐熱氣球<br />\n番紅花城<br />\n<br />\n一丁麻甩佬去 睇古蹟 風景最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再食下野咁 <br />\n<br />\nthanks thanks"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T23:07:52.000Z","msg":"土耳其國境都幾大下，11日唔會玩得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果你想走馬看花咁就無得講<br />\n<br />\n我果陣自助去12日都有好多地方未去到，淨係伊斯坦堡都夠玩3-4日，仲要計埋搭車時間呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你嫌內陸機煩既話，建議你google一下由土耳其西部去坐熱氣球果邊同棉堡要渣幾耐車，打定個底先"},{"pid":"8208f26e7205ba6b53c9d2327ccf0baf52eb81ee","tid":604215,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"搭巴士咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街熱氣球仲要睇天氣 一日應該唔夠"},{"pid":"279e98003d2ffce2c9d878aae733336d536672ad","tid":604215,"uid":43589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T04:57:56.000Z","msg":"我上年四月去咗土耳其自由行<br />\n喺伊斯坦堡留咗三日先<br />\n再搭内陸機去棉堡<br />\n要留意嘅就係佢有兩個機場，我上次比佢伏咗<br />\n要即時再買機票，不過都好平，二百幾一張<br />\n跟住搭通宵巴去cappadokya<br />\n要叫酒店幫你買定飛，都好full<br />\n留咗三日，三日都唔好天無得搭熱氣球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再搭大巴去番紅花城，留兩日<br />\n然後上ankara睇下，瞓一晚就落返istanbal留一晚第二朝走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上出名嘅嘢我都去咗，睇下行程啱唔啱你"},{"pid":"0929975797e0f3b22cdec222e686444ae8ae7db4","tid":604215,"uid":86657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"去Fethiye玩paragliding, 潛水"},{"pid":"f270649494f7721eed2d654c59eef5bd79022e39","tid":604215,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"伊斯坦堡 留到三日?<br />\n聖索非亞必去既.. 但仲有咩好行 有冇好似摩洛哥D 古城feel 既市集 咁行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c07e1e543c87b2cf8b4cba94979af7d8126687","tid":604215,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T07:38:34.000Z","msg":"坐atlasjet global 內陸機坐 business class<br />\n由 Izmir (去完以弗所返去伊斯坦堡）<br />\n800蚊港紙抵到爛<br />\n仲有 shuttle 由 以弗所接你去 Izmir 機場"},{"pid":"16c5d782321dcc59359a8229b8c25b8736b33e45","tid":604215,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f270649494f7721eed2d654c59eef5bd79022e39","tid":604215,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1